idolising their dad.</i>

02:02.160 --> 02:03.991
WHISTLE BLOWS

02:05.080 --> 02:08.116
<i>He's the strongest, funniest,
cleverest man you know.</i>

02:08.199 --> 02:09.792
- Come on, Dad!
- Go on!

02:16.840 --> 02:18.034
Get in!

02:20.400 --> 02:25.315
<i>You follow in his footsteps, hoping
one day you'll be half the man he is.</i>

02:25.400 --> 02:27.914
Yeah! Yeah!

02:32.120 --> 02:34.839
<i>But as you grow,
you begin to see his flaws.</i>

02:37.440 --> 02:41.194
<i>And then one day, you notice
he's no longer out in front.</i>

02:41.280 --> 02:42.599
