of the women of a night...

17:30.680 --> 17:32.557
MUSIC: Holding Out For A Hero
by Bonnie Tyler

17:32.640 --> 17:35.598
(All) # I need a hero! #

17:35.680 --> 17:38.194
<i>...and the unrelenting physical hardship,</i>

17:38.280 --> 17:41.238
